snippet.title: Super Mario and the Cosmic Catalyst | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
My very first project that allowed me to do whatever I wanted, so I did just that with this mod. It aims to be as unqiue as it possibly can be.
Join the Discord server: https://discord.gg/SureYz4qQK
-----------------------------------
This mod contains so many fun things such as:
- A completely new and unique story.
- New Graphics (Backgrounds, Tilesets etc.)
- New and original soundtrack. (composed by FatCat & Goatsoup.mp3)
- New custom coded elements.
- and a whole bunch more...
-----------------------------------

Thanks to everyone that has made this project come as far as it is as of right now. This wouldn't be possible without the team I work with, so a big shoutout to all the people that helped out so far. I appreciate yall so much :D.

The music for this trailer was composed by @FatCatMusic!
